+{"_type":"issue","id":"mindspec-k9a8","title":"[bug] mindspec spec create branches from local HEAD, not origin/\u003cdefault\u003e — stale base (GH #76)","description":"GitHub issue #76 (external reporter mariancristea). `mindspec spec create` creates the spec/\u003cid\u003e branch from local HEAD (local main), so a stale/unsynced local main yields a spec branched off an out-of-date base.\n\nVERIFIED still present on main:\n- internal/executor/mindspec_executor.go InitSpecWorkspace (~L86): gitutil.CreateBranch(specBranch, \"HEAD\") -\u003e git branch spec/\u003cid\u003e HEAD (internal/gitutil/gitops.go ~L96).\n\nFIX: branch from origin/\u003cdefault-branch\u003e after a fetch (detect the default branch; do not hardcode main), with graceful fallback when origin is absent/offline (fall back to local HEAD + warn). Domain: execution (+ gitutil). Small, well-scoped.","status":"open","priority":3,"issue_type":"bug","owner":"richardmaxsteel@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-06-15T16:59:00Z","created_by":"mrmaxsteel","updated_at":"2026-06-15T16:59:00Z","dependency_count":0,"dependent_count":0,"comment_count":0}
