+- [ ] `go build ./...` succeeds and the new hermetic tests pass under
+  `go test -run <Name> -timeout 120s ./...` (no LLM-harness scenario required).
+
+## Validation Proofs
+
+- `mindspec validate spec 100-ownership-gate-resolution`: 0 errors (a
